---
title: Sweet and Savory Breakfast Plum Flatbreads with Ricotta, Charred Onion, and Arugula
description: We’re taking full advantage of early summer’s stone fruit bounty and using it toward this morning-friendly flatbread. Plump plums are seared on the grill (or in a pan) to bring out their sweetness and make them extra juicy. And with tangy greens, a schmear of ricotta, and a crispy golden crust to support it all, each slice feels like a bit of sunshine you can hold in your hands.
